briefdescription.para: Template class for 3-vectors of type Quantity.

detaileddescription.para: Allows accessing and changing the elements x, y, z directly or through the corresponding get and set methods.
Angle definitions are phi [-pi, pi]: azimuthal angle in the x-y plane, 0 pointing in x-direction theta [0, pi]: zenith angle towards the z axis, 0 pointing in z-direction
